Step-by-step reasoning:
- The user wants to turn on the Family Room Lamp to 75% brightness.
- The Family Room Lamp accepts the On command [DON] with a parameter for brightness level from 0 to 100%.
- To set the brightness to 75%, send the On command with parameter 75%.
- The device name is "Family Room Lamp" and the command is "On" with parameter 75%.

{
  "routine": {
    "name": "Turn on Family Room Lamp to 75%",
    "condition": {},
    "action": {
      "device": "Family Room Lamp",
      "command": "On",
      "parameters": [
        { "name": "level", "value": 75, "uom": "percent", "precision": 1 }
      ]
    }
  }
}
